text: Liisa Winkler (b. 1978) is a Canadian fashion model. == Life and Education == Winkler grew up in Belleville, Ontario, Canada. She studied ballet at the Quinte Ballet School of Canada. Winklet was married to Ryan Boorne. They have two children. == References == Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian models Category:People from Belleville, Ontario
